title: Ep. 351 - Has Biden Already Won?
description:
Buttigieg gets a standing ovation at a Fox News Town Hall. But the polls put Joe Biden at a commanding lead over everyone, including Trump. We examine what the polls can tell us about conservatism from the U.S. to Europe all the way to Australia. Then, the MSM pretend men can get pregnant, an anti-Trump Republican humiliates himself, and revenge porn tests the limits of politics. Date: 5-20-2019
